description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit highly motivated, caring and compassionate band 6 sister/charge nurses to join the team on the Elderly Medical Wards within the Emergency and Speciality Medicine CSU.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to develop your leadership skills, to work within the multi-disciplinary team (MDT), to support the team to deliver an excellent patient centred care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be required to be an enthusiastic individual, who will support the Matron and Senior Sister to ensure expert high quality care is delivered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will also be required to take direct managerial responsibility for the clinical area in the absence of or delegated by the Senior Sister/Charge Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and develop an identified team of nurses within the ward, ensuring professional development is maintained in line with your personal appraisal objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a positive role model to the ward and MDT.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a professional, clinical resource on the ward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a good understanding of relevant local and national health agendas in relation to elderly care.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must hold the values of the Leeds Way and they will need to demonstrate commitment to providing high standards of nursing care and possess effective communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return we offer training and development opportunities to enhance and develop your skills and knowledge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post requires the successful candidates to cover the 24 hour roster period therefore, you will be expected to work nights, weekends and bank holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to have an informal discussion, or for more information, please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Matron Mashid Heydari - 07881327226&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Matron Hollie Roebuck - 07920537413&lt;/p&gt;
